description:
Format: Soft Cover, 200 pages
Availability: Ships immediately

REAL GIRLS EAT - girlosophy’s food and cooking book in the bestselling series - focuses on helping you to navigate the world of food. Girlosophy - REAL GIRLS EAT is about finding out for yourself about the food that makes you feel great, energised and ready for anything in life.

over 60 recipes;
hundreds of health and cooking tips;
body image overview;
why dieting sucks;
the danger of eating disorders;
information about the food industry today;
food travel tips; and
real girls from around the world cook up their fave foods!
DETAILS
Full colour design and printing (four colour process)
Semi gloss finish and high quality paper stock
High gloss soft cover
Gorgeous colour photography and illustrations
24cm x 24cm
ISBN: 1 74114 142 7
Winner for 'Excellence in a Soft Cover Food - Related Book' in The Vittoria Australian Food Media Awards.
